name: StandingBJ
description:
Hello there :)

this is the first release of a model I was thinking about in the past days.

As you can see from the preview images is focused mainly on one thing.

I'm still not 100% happy with the results, and I'll probably train more on this subject in the future.

Use this checkpoint in combination of vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.ckpt for best results.

None of the sample images were altered, upscaled, etc. All can be reproduced using the metadata

and here a short list of 'keywords' that were trained:

- frontal view (but is here only for future versions)

- ruined makeup

- sucking the tip of a cock

- sucking nearly half cock

- sucking half cock

- sucking more than half cock

- sucking nearly an entire cock

- sucking an entire cock

- with the tip of a cock in her mouth

- with nearly half cock in her mouth

- with half cock in her mouth

- with more than half cock in her mouth

- with nearly an entire cock in her mouth

- with an entire cock in her mouth

- a man's hand on her head

note: sucking is different from having something in mouth, so the differents prompts and results ;)

note#2: the tip, half, entire, etc.. sort of work, I'll probably need more data (and probably in the future I'll strip away some of these)

note#3: all your embedding trained on sd1.5 should work well
